snippet.title: Amber Heard on the 3 Days to Kill Red Carpet With Johnny Depp | POPSUGAR News
snippet.description:
Amber Heard was the highlight of the 3 Days to Kill red carpet in Los Angeles, but what really made her shine was that fiancé of hers that the actress brought along. That's right, the blonde beauty officially stepped out with Johnny Depp for the first time as an engaged couple, which had the whole carpet buzzing. The future Depp duo even snuck in the world's sweetest kiss in front of everyone! We also chatted with the film's stars Kevin Costner and Connie Nielsen, who had fun stories from set to share. You've got to check it out! On Becca: BCBG Max Azria jacket, Ann Taylor Necklace
